full_text: Screened by NARA, 7/11/2023 Your application for extension of your temporary stay in the United States and Form I-94 are returned without action as you failed to indicate the date your passport will expire. Your at- tension is invited to item No. 11 on your application checked in red. You are further advised extensions are granted only in cre- ments of six months and are restricted to the expiration date of your passport. I filled the date of expiration of my mother in - laws passport which is 28th july 1973.
